<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Return Policy - MoobiWorld</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="\css\returnPolicy.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="\css\shoppage_header.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("../../views/partials/user/shoppage_header") %>
    <header>
        <h1>Return Policy</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="containers">
        <section>
            <h2>Our Commitment to You</h2>
            <p>At MoobiWorld, we strive to ensure your complete satisfaction with every purchase. If you're not entirely happy with your order, we're here to help with our hassle-free return policy.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Return Eligibility</h2>
            <p>We accept returns within 30 days of delivery, provided the following conditions are met:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>The item is unused, in its original condition, and includes all original packaging and tags.</li>
                <li>The item is not a final sale or personalized product.</li>
                <li>You provide proof of purchase (e.g., order number or receipt).</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>How to Return an Item</h2>
            <p>Follow these simple steps to return your item:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Contact our customer support team at <a href="mailto:support@moobiworld.com">support@moobiworld.com</a> or call us at (123) 456-7890 to initiate a return.</li>
                <li>Provide your order number and a brief reason for the return.</li>
                <li>Pack the item securely in its original packaging and include any documentation provided.</li>
                <li>Ship the package using the prepaid return label we provide or a carrier of your choice (note: return shipping costs are the customer’s responsibility unless the item is defective or incorrect).</li>
            </ol>
            <p>Once we receive and inspect your return, we will process your refund or exchange within 5-7 business days.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Refunds</h2>
            <p>Refunds will be issued to the original payment method used for the purchase. Please note:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Original shipping costs are non-refundable.</li>
                <li>Refunds may take 3-10 business days to appear in your account, depending on your payment provider.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Exchanges</h2>
            <p>If you’d like to exchange an item for a different size, color, or style, please follow the return process and place a new order for the desired item. We’ll process the refund for the returned item once received.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Damaged or Defective Items</h2>
            <p>If you receive a damaged, defective, or incorrect item, please contact us within 7 days of delivery. We’ll provide a prepaid return label and offer a full refund or replacement at no additional cost.</p>
        </section>
        <div class="contact-info">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions about our return policy, reach out to us:</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@moobiworld.com">support@moobiworld.com</a><br>
            Phone: (123) 456-7890<br>
            Hours: Monday - Friday, 9 AM - 5 PM (EST)</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 MoobiWorld. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>